<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>التَّوضِيحُ الرَّشِيدُ فِي شَرْحِ كِتَابِ التَّوحِيدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المُذَيَّلُ بِالتَّفْنِيدِ لِشُبُهَاتِ العَنِيدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الإِمَامُ الأَلْبَانِيُّ عَنِ المَتْنِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"فَإِنَّهُ <span class="special">﵀</span> قَدْ لَخَّصَ عَقِيدَةَ السَّلَفِ فِي كِتَابِ التَّوحِيدِ المَعْرُوفِ بِهِ"</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَأْلِيفُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَبِي عَبْدِ اللهِ؛ خُلْدُونِ بنِ مَحْمُودِ بنِ نَغَوِي آل حَقُوي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَضْبُوطَةٌ بِالشَّكْلِ وَالتَّخْرِيجِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>